---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import TextFormat from "lib/helpers/TextFormat";
---

<Layout title="The buildCAP: Get the Best">
   <section
      class="container relative mt-24 flex w-full max-w-[1700px] flex-col gap-16 overflow-x-hidden px-container-base pt-4 md:gap-[10rem] md:py-[4.5rem] md:pt-[4.5rem] lg:px-container-lg xl:px-container-xl"
   >
      <div
         class="relative flex w-full flex-col gap-[1.5rem] md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] md:gap-[2.75rem]"
      >
         <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
            <p
               class="w-fit rounded-full bg-primary-1/5 p-4 px-6 text-lg font-[900] text-primary-1 md:p-4 md:px-8 md:text-2xl"
            >
               Our Mission
            </p>
            <h1
               class="max-w-[40rem] text-left text-[2rem] font-[600] leading-[130%] tracking-[0.02rem] text-secondary-2 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out md:text-[4.4rem] md:leading-[5rem] md:tracking-[0.0225rem] lg:ml-[-0.2rem]"
            >
               <TextFormat
                  text={" Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit."}
                  keyword={"amet"}
                  keywordClassName="text-primary-1 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out"
               />
            </h1>

            <div class="mb-5 flex gap-4 md:mb-0 md:ml-[-6px]">
               <a href="/" class="rounded-lg">
                  <img
                     src="/svgs/tools/android.svg"
                     class="h-[3.2rem] w-[7rem] lg:h-[5.5rem] lg:w-[6rem]"
                  />
               </a>
               <a href="/" class="rounded-lg">
                  <img
                     src="/svgs/tools/ios.svg"
                     class="h-[3.2rem] w-[7rem] lg:h-[5.5rem] lg:w-[6rem]"
                  />
               </a>
            </div>
         </div>

         <section>
            <div
               class="relative flex h-full max-h-[45rem] min-h-[25.375rem] w-full flex-col items-end justify-between rounded-3xl lg:min-h-[30.375rem] 2xl:min-h-[40.375rem]"
               style={{
                  background: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url('/images/about/hero.jpg')`,
                  backgroundSize: "cover",
                  backgroundPosition: "center",
               }}
            >
            </div>
         </section>
      </div>
      <div
         class="relative flex w-full flex-col-reverse gap-[1.5rem] md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] md:gap-[2.75rem]"
      >
         <section>
            <div
               class="relative flex h-full max-h-[45rem] min-h-[25.375rem] w-full flex-col items-end justify-between rounded-3xl lg:min-h-[30.375rem] 2xl:min-h-[40.375rem]"
               style={{
                  background: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url('/images/about/hero1.jpg')`,
                  backgroundSize: "cover",
                  backgroundPosition: "center",
               }}
            >
            </div>
         </section>
         <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col justify-center gap-6 2xl:gap-8">
            <p class="w-fit rounded-full bg-primary-1/5 p-2 px-6 text-xl font-[900] text-primary-1">
               Our Vision
            </p>
            <h1
               class="max-w-[40rem] text-left text-[2rem] font-[600] leading-[130%] tracking-[0.02rem] text-secondary-2 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out md:text-[2.5rem] md:leading-[5rem] md:tracking-[0.0225rem] lg:ml-[-0.2rem]"
            >
               <TextFormat
                  text={"A Short Story"}
                  keyword={"Story"}
                  keywordClassName="text-primary-1 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out"
               />
            </h1>
            <p class="text-[1.18rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500">
               Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Sequi illum sit, quos et
               dolor, eum, ipsum corrupti quod vero eius quo magnam nihil ipsam quidem ullam quam
               voluptate tenetur repudiandae.
            </p>

            <p class="text-[1.18rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500">
               Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Rerum, odio ipsam.
               Obcaecati deserunt sed perferendis nesciunt labore vitae nam beatae! Doloremque
               laudantium voluptate, distinctio praesentium pariatur maiores reprehenderit voluptas
               quos impedit animi, qui nisi culpa illo officiis, nulla iusto laborum minima et! Nisi
               saepe porro ipsam modi cupiditate ratione beatae!
            </p>
            <p class="text-[1.18rem] leading-[2.4rem] tracking-[0.0225rem] text-gray-500">
               Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Totam amet nulla ducimus
               vitae provident, eveniet illum nihil laudantium quo nobis blanditiis molestiae,
               minima, ea deleniti. Blanditiis commodi nostrum optio minima et! Quae dignissimos
               sint modi cum ipsa error debitis ea tempora dolor eum non dolores, omnis dolorum?
               Qui, consequatur facere?
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>

   <section class="w-full px-container-base py-[2.5rem] lg:px-container-lg xl:px-container-xl">
   </section>
</Layout>
